repository-code: "https://github.com/raphaelfh/prumo-assist"
url: "https://github.com/raphaelfh/prumo-assist"
abstract: >-
  prumo-assist is a CLI + Claude Code plugin for clinical research workflows.
  It connects Zotero (Better BibTeX), Obsidian (wiki), and the researcher's
  agent-host (Claude Code, Cursor, Codex, Gemini) around four pillars:
  bibliography management, knowledge management (wiki ingest/query/lint),
  unified capture, and academic writing (Pandoc/Typst export, peer review).
  Skills follow the universal SKILL.md format; the deterministic core is
  testable Python with forward-only schemas for long-term reproducibility.
keywords:
